{"tid":809043,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"Gwyneth Paltrow「能量石塞陰道」廣告冇根據被罰款","createTime":"2018-09-06T23:46:59.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-09T15:51:54.000Z","uid":41343,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"a57b234ae9490ac0ece61493fec531f5a70f53cb","tid":809043,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T23:46:59.000Z","msg":"美國女星桂莉芙白德露（Gwyneth Paltrow）參演《復仇者聯盟3：無限之戰》（Avengers: Infinity War）未有直接爭奪「無限聖石」，想不到她在現實中卻販賣「無限性石」惹禍！ <br />\n<br />\n桂莉芙創辦的生活網站Goop經常惹來非議，早前Goop又搞出大頭佛，賣廣告聲稱將玉石蛋與玫瑰晶蛋放進女性陰道，可以帶來「平衡荷爾蒙」、「增加女性能量」與「收陰肌」等神奇效果，售價分別是66美元（約515港元）與55美元（約429港元），而這些蛋純粹是石頭，並沒有震動功能。 <br />\n<br />\n抵唔抵買就見仁見智，不過「能量石」根本沒有科學根據，於是加州消費者保護局入稟控告Goop，Goop需要民事賠償14萬5千美元（約113萬1千港元），並刪除「能量石」廣告中沒有科學支持的描述。 <br />\n<br />\n加州消費者保護局發出聲明，力轟桂莉芙的公司：「聖克拉拉居民永遠不應該被不實廣告令健康與金錢受損。我們會警惕地保護消費者，免受那些聲稱可以提供健康好處、但沒有良好科學&hellip;&hellip;或任何科學支持的公司所害。」 <br />\n<br />\nGoop則發出聲明死撐：「我們相信對於廣告成效雙方有誠實的不同意見，本公司希望快速與和平地解決事件。這個賠償不代表Goop有任何法律責任。」 <br />\n<br />\n以往Goop已經推出過不少「問題產品」，例如一種周身貼的「能量貼紙」，聲稱是利用「美國太空總署（NASA）太空衣所用的碳傳導物質」所造，可以「平衡體內能量」，結果被NASA發出聲明踢爆造假，NASA前首席科學家Mark Shelhamer更爆粗大鬧Goop「X噏」。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20180906/mobile/bkn-20180906122414959-0906_00862_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20180906%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20180906122414959-0906_00862_001.html&d=9b3%2B2YHVjZQkmEDiOr2KC5WUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=f410f151\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20180906/mobile/bkn-20180906122414959-0906_00862_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"2b327884582f385842c8754cb3b5e612718645a9","tid":809043,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T00:02:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"864aaff06a3f9b5eb11658f64e161ca18788d4e7","tid":809043,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T00:05:53.000Z","msg":"Modern Family 間on9 公司係影射佢？"},{"pid":"57b140f785723936b53a4b7f93610222385f35e8","tid":809043,"uid":155000,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T00:14:41.000Z","msg":"佢出嚟試吓咪知work唔work"},{"pid":"e5f64e7d72f03ed6b7ea04a23cc0ad46df052057","tid":809043,"uid":59964,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T00:30:51.000Z","msg":"「收陰肌」 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f8c824c202c035fe644a736368f5e995185073b","tid":809043,"uid":116704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T00:34:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote> 而這些蛋純粹是石頭，並沒有震動功能。 </blockquote><br />\n<br />\n識震係咪就唔告<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13726522c86a15202b73ca4a535e2395fee0a7ce","tid":809043,"uid":33951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T00:35:01.000Z","msg":"NASA前首席科學家Mark Shelhamer更爆粗大鬧Goop「X噏」。 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db047ea8f65243828e553e4b7c06c17a823147e5","tid":809043,"uid":9899,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T00:40:12.000Z","msg":"係咪Iron man發明"},{"pid":"f058259bf29a81461183450e94a210fdbf2889e4","tid":809043,"uid":33104,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T01:03:03.000Z","msg":"外星科技黎，nasa班人識d咩丫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0014ab4cf04e8bd6a9dc306e967198973e804b5b","tid":809043,"uid":54927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"13726522c86a15202b73ca4a535e2395fee0a7ce","tid":809043,"uid":33951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T00:35:01.000Z","msg":"NASA前首席科學家Mark Shelhamer更爆粗大鬧Goop「X噏」。 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T12:56: